Vim Seminar

What makes Vim annoying: Modes
What makes Vim powerful: Modes
Modes:
    Normal
    Insert
    Visual
    Command-line
Basic commands
    (i)nsert text
    (Esc)-ing out of insert mode
    (hjkl) - moves cursor Left, Down, Up, Right
    (:) - Enter command-line mode
    
Help!
    Vim has awesome help built right in.
        :help or <F1>
        :help <topic, command, or keyboard key>
    
